Camoflage:

She ran through the corridors and outside.  
A short time later, she went back inside with a big look of relief 
on her face plates.  She went back to Malice's room and saw the 
other bots there. "What'd I miss?" 

Wolfblade::
She had seen Camoflage run out and walk back in. She chuckled to 
herself as she went to the lab. "Well, at least the little one is 
house broken."




--- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, robert riley <bustercross365@y...> 
wrote:
> Malice turned his attention from Wolfblade the Windlord and a tall 
femme in his doorway.  Something about her seemed familier, he stood 
and walked over to her.
> "Do I know you?" he asked simply.
> Organics stepped forward and peered into his red optics.  They 
matched, his face and voice matched, his build despite having a 
Maximal bnody matched, but one thing kept her from believeing he was 
the one she was looking for.
> "Perhaps.  I am looking for someone, who is family.  He has a 
brother fallen to darkness, and a long lost adoptive sister.  He was 
a Decepticon, Autobot, and some now say he is a most ruthless bounty 
hunter.  Do you know of anyone like this bot?"
> Malice stared the femme back, taking in everything she said.  Then 
it hit him like a freight train.  
>  
> This is his lost sister, Organics.
> "Organics?" the bounty hunter asked.
> The femme threw her arms around around his neck.
> "Oh Neutronics!  Where have you been?"
> "Where have I been?  You were the one who disappeared without a 
trace.  How have you been in the past three hundred years?"
> He realized he neglected to introduce everyone.
> "Wolfblade, please meet my long lost sister, Organics." he said as 
he wheeled around and presented his half sister to Wolfblade.
